name: Pocketfriend Project - What is a friend? (Canceled)
blurb: Pocketfriend Mission - Putting the friend in your pocket, being the sidekick of your life.

rewards.reward: Digital Pack Rewards. \r\nOne of the Pocketfriend team members will give you a quick Skype meeting to say Hi and Thank you. Your choice if you want to, but we can also let you know how the development is going and plan another time to have a meeting for you to get a quick update.

Acknowledgment Pack Rewards.\r\nThank you, every bit helps and your contribution is amazing! We\u2019ll acknowledge you through a social media post and email you a BIG thank you. \r\nIncludes Digital Pack Rewards

Sincere Friend Pack Rewards. \r\nYou\u2019ll be one of the first to know when the Pocket Friend app is launched, with exclusive details sent you via email that show behind the scenes during the development process.\r\nIncludes Acknowledgment Pack Rewards

Buddy Pack Rewards.
You will be sent a one of a kind Pocketfriend key ring. These will never be given to anyone outside of this Kickstarter campaign. 
Includes Sincere Friend Pack Rewards
$10 extra is for the postage to send the Pocketfriend Key Ring, only outside of Australia.

Mate Pack Reward.
Send the Pocketfriend team 3 photos or a video of 2 minutes or less and we’ll upload it to the Pocketfriend Facebook page and it will stay on the Pocketfriend website for 6 months. Let us know what is a friend, in your opinion and we’ll share it to the world?
Includes Buddy Pack Rewards
$10 extra is for the postage to send the Pocketfriend Key Ring, only outside of Australia.

Bestfriends Pack Reward.
Be a Pocketfriend for 3 months in the Pocketfriend app. We’ll send you an email with a comprehensive profile survey attached and details for you to complete. You will be a Pocketfriend potentially for the world to choose and use for their lifestyle and needs. 
Includes Mate Pack Rewards
$10 extra is for the postage to send the Pocketfriend Key Ring, only outside of Australia.

Experience Pack Reward.
2 nights’ premium accommodation in Perth, Western Australia. Meet the Pocketfriend lead developer and team. Stay in a Penthouse Apartment or a luxury Hotel and enjoy an experience of a lifetime. Share your ideas and opinions and feel a part of the team during your experience. Valid between June 30 2014 to June 30 2015, airfares not included but breakfasts, lunches and dinners are.
Includes Bestfriends Pack Rewards
$10 extra is for the postage to send the Pocketfriend Key Ring, only outside of Australia.

Vision Pack Reward.
4 nights’ premium accommodation in Perth, Western Australia. Meet the Pocketfriend lead developer and team that are behind the Pocketfriend project. Stay in a Penthouse Apartment or a luxury Hotel and enjoy an experience of a lifetime sightseeing around Perth toured by a Business Executive. Including; Revolving Restaurant, Rottnest Island, Kalgoolie Superpit and Margaret River Winery. Let us know what you think, share your opinions and be a part of a brainstorm session were you feel a part of the team throughout your whole experience. Valid between June 30 2014 to June 30 2015, airfares not included but breakfasts, lunches and dinners are.
Includes Bestfriends Pack Rewards
$10 extra is for the postage to send the Pocketfriend Key Ring, only outside of Australia.
